@page "/mineawarevr-privacy-policy"

<PageTitle>Privacy Policy for MineAware VR - Fish Sauce Games</PageTitle>

<section class="privacy">
    <h1>Privacy Policy for MineAware VR</h1>
    <p class="effective-date"><strong>Effective Date: 2024-07-10</strong></p>

    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to MineAware VR. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our VR app.</p>

    <h2>2. Data Collection</h2>
    <p>We do not collect any personal or non-personal data from users of the MineAware VR app. We respect your privacy and have designed our app to ensure that your information remains secure and private.</p>

    <h2>3. Data Usage</h2>
    <p>Since we do not collect any data, we do not use, share, or disclose any personal or non-personal data from our users.</p>

    <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>MineAware VR does not integrate with any third-party services that collect, store, or use data from our users. Your usage of the app is entirely private and secure.</p>

    <h2>5. Device Information</h2>
    <p>We do not collect or store any information from your device. Any data generated by the app remains on your device and is not transmitted to any servers or third parties.</p>

    <h2>6. Security</h2>
    <p>While we do not collect any data, we are committed to maintaining the security and integrity of our app to ensure a safe user experience.</p>

    <h2>7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. These changes are effective immediately upon posting.</p>

    <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
    <p>SACL Safer Access Consulting Lmtd</p>
    <p>Justin@FishSauceGames.com</p>

    <p>Thank you for using MineAware VR. We are committed to ensuring your privacy and providing a secure experience.</p>
</section>
